name: British Antarctic Survey De Havilland Canada Dash 7 Arrival at Calgary Airport
description:
A special visitor from back in April, our annual visit from the British Antarctic Survey's De Havilland Canada Dash 7! This distinctive quad-turboprop is always a pleasure to see, as they become rarer and rarer.

Hope you all enjoy this quick spotting video! My next upload will be a very exciting trip report... Follow me on Twitter and Instagram if you'd like a sneak peek ;)
